{"tid":549081,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"六核對決 AMD RYZEN 5 1600 VS INTEL CORE I5-8400","createTime":"2018-02-03T09:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T18:07:46.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4157f326d8e90f759dc7cbee300a11a4c5dec23c","tid":549081,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T09:16:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.xfastest.com/review/review-focus/45710/amd-ryzen-5-1600-vs-intel-core-i5-8400-review/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Freview%2Freview-focus%2F45710%2Famd-ryzen-5-1600-vs-intel-core-i5-8400-review%2F&d=v6tcZVhR5zdeH8CLGWrrsf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=22b3c33e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.xfastest.com/review/review-focus/45710/amd-ryzen-5-1600-vs-intel-core-i5-8400-review/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>點睇</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f28cf8554e48e00c8e54add2abb51ecc7d5b1f9b","tid":549081,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T09:16:38.000Z","msg":"AMD 主流級的 Ryzen 5 系列處理器 1600，有著 6 核心 12 執行緒的多工處理能力，以及 L3 16MB 快取、65W TDP 設計，核心時脈基準 3.2GHz、Boost 3.6GHz 的加速時脈，況且 Ryzen 全系列皆可超頻，讓 1600 有著上超 4GHz 的能力；而台灣定價 Ryzen 5 1600 則要價 7,300 元左右。<br />\n<br />\n對比的 Intel 同主流級的 Core i5-8400 處理器，亦有著 6 顆處理器核心，但是 Intel 關閉 HT 多線程技術，因此 i5-8400 為 6 核心 6 執行緒處理器，核心基準時脈 2.8GHz，但加速時脈可達 4GHz；另一方面，Intel 全球定價策略下，i5-8400 相對便宜 6,500 元左右的價格，即可擁有真實 6 核心。<br />\n<br />\n此次以兩家價位較接近的 6 核心處理器，來比較 CPU 性能與整平台的電腦表現，測試平台如下表所示：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-1.jpg&h=36aa7362&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ddb0f80f1f2a5b228103c58709eaf457602d4ac0","tid":549081,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T09:17:20.000Z","msg":"測試時，i5-8400（無法超頻）採用主機板預設設定，並透過 XMP 設定記憶體為 3200MHz；Ryzen 5 1600 除了採主機板預設 3.4GHz 測試之外，亦加入使用 Noctua NH-D15S 散熱器超頻至 4GHz 測試；讓玩家了解到，i5-8400 對上 Ryzen 5 1600 的基本性能表現，以及 Ryzen 小超小賺的美好。"},{"pid":"ad1be8f2908e4917c3ef7cdb03bdea53cef98007","tid":549081,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T09:19:56.000Z","msg":"首先對於處理器的單核、多核性能測試，CPU-Z Bench 測試中，單核性能上 Ryzen 5 1600 以 414 分落後於 i5-8400的 465 分，及使 Ryzen 5 1600 超頻至 3.9GHz，也難在單核心表現上扳回一成；但是，多線程的測試上，跑預設時脈的 Ryzen 5 1600 即輕鬆贏過 i5-8400，超頻至 3.9GHz 後多線程性能更有著顯著提升。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-2.jpg&h=b8257481&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&uarr; CPU-Z Bench 分數越高越好。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCPUmark 99 測試，則是評鑑處理器的單核性能，因此這項目由 i5-8400 較高的時脈與單核性能領先。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-3.jpg&h=748f741f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&uarr; CPUmark 99 分數越高越好。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nwPrime 則是透過多線程計算數學平方根，問題難度分為 32M 與 1024M，計算時間月短著有著越高的性能。在預設 4T 測試上 i5-8400 憑著高時脈還是獲得領先，只不過當線程改以 6T、12T 時，可見 Ryzen 5 1600 支援多線程技術，可讓計算時間大幅縮短，提升多核心運算性能。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-4.jpg&h=7e4a7d06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&uarr; wPrime 時間越短越好。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCINEBENCH R15 則可測試，處理器單核心與多核心渲染貼圖的性能。以單核心測試時，i5-8400 依舊領先於 Ryzen 5 1600，但當使用多核心測試時則反了過來，Ryzen 5 1600 預設有著 1150 cb 的多核心性能，超頻後更來到 1311 cb。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-5.jpg&h=b2e07d98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&uarr; CINEBENCH R15 分數越高越好。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCorona Benchmark 則是相當容易操作的測試工具，主要是透過 CPU 運算光線追蹤的渲染圖像，評分為計時以秒為單位。從測試結果來看，Ryzen 5 1600 預設就有 188 秒的成績，在超頻 3.9GHz 後運算速度亦縮短至 168 秒，比起 i5-8400 的 236 秒還快上許多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-6.jpg&h=3c6f7a7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&uarr; Corona Benchmark 時間越短越好。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nV-Ray Benchmark 可分別測試電腦的 CPU 與 GPU，對光線追蹤的渲染圖像的運算速度，評分為計時以秒為單位。此測試下，Ryzen 5 1600 預設 177 秒即可完成測試，超頻 3.9GHz 後更有縮短至 101 秒，而相對僅只有 6 核心 6 線程的 i5-8400 則需花費 130 秒才能完成測試。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-7.jpg&h=f0c57ae5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&uarr; V-Ray Benchmark 時間越短越好。</span>"},{"pid":"5f1e91d1646d5b6da2995db921c78019ba7144c3","tid":549081,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T09:20:39.000Z","msg":"記憶體測試，透過 AIDA64 進行基本對記憶體的讀、寫、複製與延遲測試。此次測試時，皆使用相同雙通道記憶體，並設定為 3200MHz 記憶體時脈，從測試來看 Ryzen 平台的記憶體延遲還是較高，但記憶體讀寫等性能有追上 Intel 平台。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-8.jpg&h=29e56849&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&uarr; 記憶體測試，速度越快越好。</span>"},{"pid":"a2bfcc4d02cdb7620f1570fb48321b167710750b","tid":549081,"uid":62985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T09:22:01.000Z","msg":"普通用家<br />\n用咩軟件或遊戲先有分別？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4df1f332702d052613908f374e7cc34977612ac","tid":549081,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T09:22:28.000Z","msg":"WinRAR 壓縮軟體測試下，Ryzen 5 1600 在超頻後與 i5-8400 表現相近，皆有著 10000 KB/s 的處理速度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-9.jpg&h=e54f68d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&uarr; WinRAR 分數越高越好。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7-Zip 壓縮測試，則是 Ryzen 5 1600 領先於 i5-8400，可見多核心、多線程數高的處理器，在多核心應用上還是有著絕對優勢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-10.jpg&h=1594cdc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&uarr; 7-Zip 分數越高越好。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n影音轉檔方面，則是相當吃重多核心性能，測試使用 X264 / X265 FHD Benchmark 進行。Ryzen 5 1600 在 x264 編碼上性能強過 i5-8400，但是在 x265 編碼上，Intel 有著指令支援，因此性能高於 Ryzen 5 1600。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-11.jpg&h=d93ecd5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&uarr; X264 / X265 FHD Benchmark 分數越高越好。</span>"},{"pid":"c7281d2909718be423cb60dfd39b8d455e9468eb","tid":549081,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T09:23:01.000Z","msg":"PCMark 10 測試，可分別針對 Essentials 基本電腦工作，如 App 啟動速度、視訊會議、網頁瀏覽性能進行評分，而 Productivity 生產力測試，則以試算表與文書工作為測試項目，至於 Digital Content Creation 影像內容創作上，則是以相片 / 影片編輯和渲染與可視化進行測，最後 Gaming 測試則是分別計算電腦物理運算與繪圖分數。<br />\n<br />\n從 Overall 總分來看，Ryzen 5 1600 在超頻後與 i5-8400 旗鼓相當，整體分數都在 7000 分左右，可見一斑電腦工作，還是需要高時脈的處理器來支援。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-12.jpg&h=57b1cabe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&uarr; PCMark 10 分數越高越好。</span>"},{"pid":"539d67a68ee76abf15d55d9ef31a2b34c446b2a5","tid":549081,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T09:23:25.000Z","msg":"3DMark 繪圖效能測試方面，則分為總分與物理運算 CPU 得分。Ryzen 5 1600 亦在超頻後於總分與物理分數上技壓群雄，對於遊戲玩家這兩顆處理器都有相當好的性能，可發揮出顯示卡的性能；但另一方面，Ryzen 5 1600 有著多線程技術，更可在遊戲同時進行直播任務。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-13.jpg&h=9b1bca20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&uarr; 3DMark 分數越高越好。</span>"},{"pid":"8a16b333a28425b9f43762ec4df1cc196182f080","tid":549081,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T09:24:02.000Z","msg":"Unigine Benchmrk 則是採用自家的遊戲引擎開發的測試工具，新的 Superposition 1080p High 測試中，兩者獲得相近的平均 80 fps 表現；而其餘兩款 Heaven 與 Valley 測試兩者差異不到 5 fps。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-15.jpg&h=5d74c3a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&uarr; Unigine Benchmrk fps 越高越好。</span>"},{"pid":"e16ff88b8ff9bcde919d9e54380a8232de96bf8a","tid":549081,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T09:24:38.000Z","msg":"遊戲測試，則以《鬥陣特工》、《俠盜獵車手 5》與《絕地求生 PUBG》進行測試，性能表現上 i5-8400 獲得較高的 fps 性能，但與 Ryzen 5 1600 差距不到 10 fps<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400/AMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-1600-Intel-Core-i5-8400-16.jpg&h=d3fbc444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&uarr; 遊戲測試 fps 數越高越好。</span>"},{"pid":"b789e41cb935c30521a2d53980066c1390fa6921","tid":549081,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T09:28:28.000Z","msg":"這波 6 核心對決，i5-8400 憑著高時脈與單核心性能，還是在部分單線程、單核測試上贏過對手，但是 Ryzen 5 1600 憑著多線程技術 6 核心 12 執行緒，於多核心測試上碾過對手，況且 Ryzen 可超頻的設計，將 Ryzen 5 1600 超頻至 3.9GHz，不僅可穩定跑完測試，並有著更強悍的多核心性能。<br />\n<br />\n對於主流級玩家，Ryzen 5 1600 優勢在於可小超頻，並有著多線程技術更強的多核性能，相對 i5-8400 則是強在單核與預設時脈高；兩者性能各有千秋，但考量到香港定價，Ryzen 5 1600 還是有著不少優勢，且 AMD 預計在 4 月推出第 2 代 Ryzen 處理器，屆時肯定有著更高的時脈設定與性能提升，就讓我們技術關注 AMD 與 Intel 的多核大戰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRyzen 5 1600：HKD1475<br />\n<br />\ni5 8400：HKD1570<br />\n<br />\n價格來源：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.jumbo-computer.com/pricelist.aspx?id=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jumbo-computer.com%2Fpricelist.aspx%3Fid%3D3&d=v6tcZVhR5zdeH8CLGWrrsf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=387c4e8e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jumbo-computer.com/pricelist.aspx?id=3</a>"},{"pid":"2eb846d91fb7b3805e77418487e727b01bfa6f56","tid":549081,"uid":13622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T09:53:38.000Z","msg":"Intel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f774d986f605a1dca9159a3c52768939b3d62bef","tid":549081,"uid":38820,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T10:26:06.000Z","msg":"In AMD &amp; 悠二, we trust!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e44bc331dd6b5e939edf1f0ddec7a31a14b55ed","tid":549081,"uid":40428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T10:35:07.000Z","msg":"等睇下代AMD <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a7383061cc19d66377c84419a56d80ee19bf11","tid":549081,"uid":156005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T10:38:16.000Z","msg":"AMD單係塊板都平d"},{"pid":"a2dbc94ec7972ed2e8938761537e9d70da1296f9","tid":549081,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c4a7383061cc19d66377c84419a56d80ee19bf11","tid":549081,"uid":156005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T10:38:16.000Z","msg":"AMD單係塊板都平d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T10:43:16.000Z","msg":"呢個先係重點"},{"pid":"d74981c1a768ab0be16aebb99d9d928fbc5d7d2c","tid":549081,"uid":22817,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T12:31:31.000Z","msg":"AMD,Yes!"},{"pid":"84ebb67c1686b57